Package seng202.group5.information

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Customer
    The Customer class holds information about each Customer who is considered a member and have a unique ID and an amount of loyalty points that can purchase food with.
    Customers
    Holds the list of customers, allows JAXB to easily import and export the customers data
    CustomerSettings
    Holds the settings when initialising a customer.
    Ingredient
    The Ingredient class records all the base data for each ingredient in the database which include its name, price, category, id and its price.
    MenuItem
    This class contains methods to update the stock, removes the stock , calculates the making and selling price for the menu item.
    Recipe
    The Recipe class records all the recipes along with the steps that are stored in the database.
    Transaction
    The Transaction class records past orders and if they were refunded;
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    DietEnum
    An enum for tracking whether or not recipes meet certain dietary requirements
    TypeEnum
    An enum for specifying what type of item a menu item is
